Product name: Drawing of children from Germaine Bouret - 1940 - Litography
Description:
Lithography of a drawing from Germaine Bouret (1907-1953), very rare to find in this dimension (length 50cm, 32.5cm width).
Germaine Bouret was born in Paris May 29, 1907, a Berry father and an English mother. Very young she is attracted by the drawing and in 1922, at age 15, she won a national competition in this discipline. She took drawing classes in a reputable school, rue Madame in Paris, then she returned for a short time as a fashion designer at the fashion house Lanvin. In 1926 and 1927 she participated in the "Salon des Humoristes" and exhibits two drawings next to the famous illustrators of the time.
At 20, in 1927, she created her company as "Bouret Editions" Author-Publisher. Her first works are for menus and prints. In 1927 she illustrated her first book, "Touche à tout, ses tragiques mésaventures", published by Fernand Nathan.
Quickly she specializes in postcard and prints in different formats, which will adorn, for generations, the walls of most French households. In 1937 she was Deputy Secretary General in the Arts and Techniques category for the Universal Exhibition in Paris. 
In the early forties Walt Disney, recruiting designers in Europe for its studios in the US, made him an offer she refused. After his death it will say of her: "She was the best designer in the world".  Mainly drawing children, she was asked to work on youth. She also worked for advertising. Lesieur has used its work for flyers and recipe cards, Vittelloise, she also created the slogan "water that sings and dances" Jacquemaire for its boxes illustration Blédine of flour well Patisfrance supply confectioners, the little boy and the slogan "Eat cakes often, it's delicious and nutritious" are known to all. It should be noted that this company is still using this today, for over fifty years. While other companies are to his credit including Maggi, Nestle, Kohler, Petit Bateau, to name only the best known.

Product name: Male Dog Belly Band - Dog Diaper - Dog Potty Training Aid - house breaking - incontienence wrap - fleece - X Small to X Large - CUSTOM ORDER
Description:
Great for dogs and puppies working on house breaking, dogs who mark, senior dogs, or dogs with incontinence. To make this super absorbent, line interior of band with a self adhesive feminine napkin or adult urine absorbing pad. 
This listing is for one custom sized belly band made to fit your puppy or dog. 
WHEN YOU CHECKOUT, PLEASE ADD TO THE CHECKOUT NOTES: 
"Straight" or "Contoured" 
I will make your bands straight unless otherwise specified. Please also note any special requests such as a larger or smaller width (1 extra inch smaller or larger is included at no charge.) Make any other requests you would like. I always review the notes before I begin work on your belly band. 
Size Chart: 
Your dog's girth should fall in the middle of the suggested girth measurements below. As you get toward the end of the range, some velcro will be exposed. Example:  If your dog measures 12", select the small band.
Extra Small  15" x 3"         Fits dogs with a girth of 9" - 13"       
Small  16.5" x 4"                Fits dogs with a girth of 10 - 15"      
Medium  21.5" x 4"           Fits dogs with a girth of 14" - 20"     
Large  26.5" x 5"               Fits dogs with a girth of 19" - 25"     
Extra Lg  32" x 6"              Fits dogs with a girth of 24" - 30"  
Custom sizes and options are always available, just send me a convo and I'll make up a special order just for you. I can also sew in an absorbent pad.
********************************IMPORTANT***********************************
Please provide your DOG'S GIRTH MEASUREMENTS in your checkout notes
Dog sizes are NOT standardized, so you must measure your dog to get a proper fit for this diaper. If you do not provide your dog's measurement in your checkout notes, I am unable to accept a return or exchange for a sizing issue. For sanitary reasons, I can't resell a returned diaper.
It is my top priority to get you a proper fitting diaper. I hate to see people disappointed when items don't fit. I stand behind my products 100% and will make it right if there is an error on my part. Please help me to provide the best experience possible by providing your dog's measurement. I know it's a pain, I always hate measuring my own dogs - but do it just this once. Your pup will thank you!
*********************************************************************************
Features:
-100% cotton exterior fabric
-Soft absorbent fleece interior fabric
-Straight bands have 2 strips of 4" of hook and loop tape. Contoured bands have a wider 3" of hook and loop. This allows for an adjustable fit, soft side of the hook and loop always faces the tummy.
-I only use Gutermann polyester thread. This durable high quality thread will not pull moisture up to the cotton layer as cotton thread will tend to do.
- Quality, reinforced stitches
- Elastic - If selected, elastic is sewn on either side of the band and works much like the elastic in a baby diaper. It holds the band closer and fits all the contours of your dogs body. I recommend elastic for smooth coated or barrel chested dogs. I can also make the elastic smaller on one side, which has helped some very barrel chested dogs in the past. Just let me know in your checkout notes. Also consider adding an inch or two to your girth measurement if you do not like your elastic tight. If you are unsure, just send me a convo and I'll help you get the perfect size. 
- Waterproof PUL - If selected, the waterproof PUL layer is sewn between your fabric layers. You won't see it. Consider adding an inch to your width. If your dog has a large or forward set penis, he may urinate too close to the edge of the band and the cotton will pull the moisture up at the very edges. An extra inch can make all the difference in solving this problem. This PUL is the same stuff we use in human diapers.

Care:
Close the hook and loop tape before washing to avoid the hooks attaching to other items or collecting threads in them.
Machine wash in cool or warm water. Air dry for longest life. If you use the dryer, use the lowest setting possible.
Please use a color catcher sheet if you wash these with other items. The fleece can shed some color in the first few washings.
To remove urine odor, add regular vinegar to the rinse cycle. I also like the product OdoBan. I add both of these to the "softener" section of my washing machine.

This soap provides gentle exfoliation, removes dirt and other impurities, suitable for cleansing normal and dry skin on your face or body, it can be used as a regular cleanser.
Moroccan soap or savon Beldi is a Moroccan style as a traditional soap used in the Hammam Spa ritual. Over time, it became popular in Mediterranean countries and Europe, due to its unique quality and efficiency as a gentle moisturizing natural soap. Our products are high quality Premium grade organic all natural Beldi soap is made with the highest quality olive oil, castor oil, Apricot oil, oatmeal powder, honey, milk, oil of apricot pits, patchouli essential oil, orange essential oil and essential oil of ylang-ylang. This soap gel paste has a viscous consistency and a pleasant natural aroma . Moroccan Beldi Savon has a unique ability to open the pores and remove dead skin cells, making skin radiant, soft and smooth.
* Oatmeal is suitable for all skin types, even for sensitive skin due to its anti-inflammatory properties.
* Oats
- contains polysaccharides, which have a gel-like texture in combination with humidity. This gel leaves a protective layer on the skin that seals in skin's natural moisture and provides additional nutrients. The proteins in oats also improve the functionality of the skin barrier by increasing the production filaggrin, an important element of the barrier function of the skin. The oats in this soap helps to retain its natural moisture, while other assets can help replenish the moisture level. The starch in the oats can absorb the water and bind it to the skin. A rich source of avenanthramides, unique antioxidants not found in other plant sources. Avenanthramides are the main assets in oats, which reduce redness and inflammation, especially irritation from excessive exposure to the sun. Oats contains saponins, which are the perfect gentle cleanser for sensitive skin, because they absorb dirt and debris on the skin surface. Meaning that dirt can easily be rinsed off without disrupting the skin barrier.
Method of application: Apply thin layer on wet/damp skin, leave 1 to 10 minutes, then rinse, gently massage using your exfoliating gloves or a loofah or office, and finish in a hot bath or a warm shower.It will leave your skin clean, radiant, smooth and soft.For best results, use with Spa bath,shower and steam bath.
Weekly exfoliation is recommended. Or use as a regular cleanser.
To avoid eyes. External use.
INGREDIENTS
Saponified oil: Extra virgin Olive, Castor Oil, SF - 10% Apricot Kernel oil, oatmeal powder, honey, milk powder apricot kernel oil, essential oil patchouli, essential oil orange, and essential oil ylang-ylang.

We select our ingredients and create our products with the utmost of integrity and will treat you as we would family. Your satisfaction drives our inspiration, and we want to share with you what truly natural, handmade holistic products can do for you.

My soaps are composed of 100% all natural and vegan friendly ingredients which are completely biodegradable and safe for all skin types. Product name: Fountain Pen, Handcrafted Pen, One of a Kind Gift, Volcanic Rock, Calligraphy Pen, Hand Turned, Gift for Men, Custom Pens, Handmade Pen
Description:
This unique fountain pen is a one of a kind. The pen has been handmade with real volcanic material, and has Rhodium with Black Titanium Accents. The fountain pen also features an Iridium Point Germany nib and comes with a deluxe pressed metal velvet case making it an ideal gift.
The M3 Lava used to create the body of this gorgeous pen is produced with real volcanic material from ancient dormant volcanoes found in the Southwest, USA. The volcanic ash is found in a variety of natural colors allowing for dramatic color contrast with other materials especially metal. Once reconstructed by the M3 process, the new molecular structure of the Lava is extremely strong, heat resistant and exhibits a beautiful, durable natural surface.
Macro-Molecular Materials (M3) are part of the new breed of new age designer materials that make everything from the Stealth Bomber to the International Space Station possible. These materials are made with high purity metals and other exotic elements that have been deconstructed to the macro-molecular level, homogenously combined and then reconstructed with highly refined proprietary chemical binders.  Objects produced from M3 Mokume will literally last forever.
The fountain pen also comes with a disposable cartridge and a fountain pen pump converter. We offer 2 x blue or 2 x black, or a combination of ink cartridge at no extra charge, please select your colour.

Inchoo isn’t a simple ornamentation, it’s a jewel combining romanticism and eccentricity; it’s the mystery of a feminine symbol that’s not afraid to show a darker side. Every piece becomes a unique poem, unveiling force and finesse through noble materials.
Listing is for 1 Sterling Silver Bar Fake Lip Ring.
Bar mesures a little less that 20mm.
Inchoo traces its place in elegance and an unchanging contrast between gothic curves and popular culture that blends with imagination. In a world where unicorns caress rose thorns, where birds sing their way onto deer antlers, comes a symbol of a woman who is willing to show her darker side. Rawk calls to the mystery that flows with delicate curves in hair and chiaroscuro eyes. Aspire looks and envy at the rhythm of your heels and embrace your inner enchantress. Inchoo isn’t a simple ornamentation, it’s the symbioses of Romantisme and the extravagance that are within your charm.
Astrid loves baroque inspired environments, the dark and gothic inspired looks but also the highly feminine and glamour tastes of it. Her world flirts around skulls, taxidermy and macabre inspired themes as much as big statement shiny and haute couture jewelry. She loves to create new pieces using the body as a canvas. Inchoo Bijoux is for her, the perfect balance between gothic and glamour jewelry. Hope you enjoy them as much as she loves making them for you ! 
Care
Jewellery in Sterling silver and Bronze are easy maintenance. You can keep them clean by cleansing them with an old tooth brush and some Dawn (dish soap without Phosphate). To keep them shiny and a premature tarnish, keep them in hermetic bags and away from plants, as they emanate big concentrations of oxygen.

**Some Friendly Advise On Stretching***
As a professional body piercer, I recommend my clients stretching their ear lobes to not skip sizes and to "upsize" (stretch to the next size) once every 2 months only to allow sufficient healing time and minimise the risk of blow outs and scarring. Also to have a soak in a hot bath or shower before hand to help elastic the skin and to apply non flavored vaseline to the jewelry to help it to slide into the ear easier and cause less trauma to the area.

----- CARE INSTRUCTIONS ------
All our moccasins come in a protective dustbag.
To clean the soles simply get a damp cloth or a baby wipe and lightly rub off any excess dirt.
------ SIZING ------
We make limited runs of each of our products. To purchase please let us know what size you would like.
Follow these simple instructions to determine the best shoe size to buy.
1. Measure your child's foot from the tip of their big toe to the back of their heel
2. We advise that you add an extra 1/2cm to allow for room
3. Compare your measurement with the size chart shown below (ages are approximates)
XS : 10.5cm : 0-6 months
S : 11.5cm : 6-9 months
M : 12.5cm : 9-12 months
L : 13.5cm : 12-18 months 
XL : 14.5cm : 18-24 months
